Resource Profile: 評估問卷

Official URL: http://example.org/StructureDefinition/SPACQuestionnaire Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-10-28 Computable Name: SPACQuestionnaire

評估問卷的結構化定義，實際問卷內容請參考Structure: Questionnaire，可依據前者內容做為範本進行擴充

Usages:

  • Examples for this Profile: ARATQuestionnaire, Questionnaire/BarthelQuestionnaireInstance, FMAUEMotorQuestionnaire, FMAUESensoryQuestionnaire... Show 5 more, IDALQuestionnaireInstance, Questionnaire/MASQuestionnaireInstance, Questionnaire/MMSEQuestionnaireInstance, Questionnaire/MRCQuestionnaireInstance and WMFTQuestionnaire

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
